      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MODELING (5) scored two back by a space then was last start always well back and could manage only a 6 length 8th at this track (18.40). The form out of his last race has been franked. Should bounce back. DESPICABLE PEDRO (1) used the rails draw to advantage to get home last time at Maitland over 400m (22.41), scoring by 2.25 lengths. Expected to be in the finish. REALLY SAVAGE (4) had won two in a row before finishing sixth (17.86) last time at this track. Form here is sound including three wins. Boasts three wins from five starts out of this box. Deserves plenty of respect. EXPLORE (2) can run a bold race on best form.",
